## School funds and activities

In each sampled village, the largest government school with primary sections is visited on the day of the survey. Information about schools in this report is based on these visits.

### Table 12: Trends over time
% Schools reporting receipt of SSA grants – Full financial year

| Full financial year | Maintenance grant | Development grant | TLM grant |
|---------------------|-------------------|-------------------|-----------|
| April 2010 to March 2011 | 72.5 | 62.1 | 75.3 |
| April 2011 to March 2012 | 85.2 | 72.5 | 88.5 |
| April 2013 to March 2014 | 78.5 | 55.2 | 32.5 |
| April 2015 to March 2016 | 80.2 | 62.5 | 18.5 |

